      "widgets_values": [
        "**ℹ️ Group notes**\n• **Load Diffusion Model** — the Krea 2 checkpoint (Turbo FP8 recommended).\n• **Load CLIP** — Qwen3VL-4B text encoder, keep type **krea2**.\n• **Load VAE** — Qwen-Image VAE used by Krea 2.\n• **Lora Loader** — optional style/character LoRA on top of the base model.\n• **Star Krea2 Unbound** — StarNodes patch that lets the Krea 2 model answer the prompt freely, without its built-in boundaries."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        720,
        300
      ],
      "size": [
        440,
        210
      ],
      "flags": {},
