        "# 🦦 Standard Krea 2 Set & SeedVR2 - Download Guide\n\nWelcome to the official model download guide for the standard **Krea 2** set and the **SeedVR2 Upscaler** (Group ④). \n\nPlease download the models using the links below and place them in the correct directories within your ComfyUI installation.\n\n---\n\n## 📥 1. Standard Krea 2 Set\n\n**Repository:** [Comfy-Org/Krea-2](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Krea-2)\n\n### Diffusion Model\n* **File:** `krea2_turbo_fp8_scaled.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Krea-2/resolve/main/diffusion_models/krea2_turbo_fp8_scaled.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`\n\n### Text Encoder (CLIP)\n* **File:** `qwen3vl_4b_fp8_scaled.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Krea-2/resolve/main/text_encoders/qwen3vl_4b_fp8_scaled.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/`\n\n### VAE\n* **File:** `qwen_image_vae.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Krea-2/resolve/main/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/vae/`\n\n### Optional Style LoRAs\n* **Directory:** `ComfyUI/models/loras/`\n* **Download:** [Browse Krea 2 LoRAs here](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Krea-2/tree/main/loras)\n\n---\n\n## 📥 2. SeedVR2 Upscaler (Group ④)\n\n**Repository:** [Comfy-Org/SeedVR2](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/SeedVR2)\n\n### Diffusion Model\n* **File:** `seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/SeedVR2/resolve/main/seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`\n\n### VAE\n* **File:** `ema_vae_fp16.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / numz](https://huggingface.co/numz/SeedVR2_comfyUI/resolve/main/ema_vae_fp16.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/vae/`\n\n---\n\n## 📂 Folder Structure Overview\n\nMake sure your directories look like this before launching ComfyUI:\n\n```text\nComfyUI/\n├── models/\n│   ├── diffusion_models/\n│   │   ├── krea2_turbo_fp8_scaled.safetensors\n│   │   └── seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors\n│   ├── text_encoders/\n│   │   └── qwen3vl_4b_fp8_scaled.safetensors\n│   ├── vae/\n│   │   ├── qwen_image_vae.safetensors\n│   │   └── ema_vae_fp16.safetensors\n│   └── loras/\n│       └── [Downloaded Krea 2 LoRA files]\n```\n\n*Happy generating from your favorite fluffy purple otter!* 🦦✨"
